1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,560
I should have left sooner.

2
00:00:01,560 --> 00:00:04,520
My mum still checks under the bed every night.

3
00:00:04,520 --> 00:00:08,720
After hearing what happened in 1993, I understand why.

4
00:00:08,720 --> 00:00:10,880
I remember Hale, my name is Ben,

5
00:00:10,880 --> 00:00:13,960
and I want to tell you a story my mother cat used to tell me

6
00:00:13,960 --> 00:00:16,400
whenever I misbehaved the story of what happened

7
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:18,280
to her sister, Sharon.

8
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:21,040
I remember cat swore it really happened.

9
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:24,600
I remember the older I get, the more I believe her.

10
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:29,440
I remember it was 1993 in rural New South Wales, Australia.

11
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:33,120
I remember cat was 12, living in an old house that looked nice,

12
00:00:33,120 --> 00:00:35,440
but felt wrong.

13
00:00:35,440 --> 00:00:37,680
I remember her family was about to move

14
00:00:37,680 --> 00:00:39,840
because the house was no longer suitable,

15
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:42,280
or at least that's what her mother said.

16
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:45,040
I remember cats suspected the truth.

17
00:00:45,040 --> 00:00:48,080
Her strict religious mother believed the house was evil.
